| `.planning/` | Symlink into `gsd-docs/` — shared project context + personal plans |
| `gsd-docs/` | Clone of `parloa/gsd-docs` (`docs` branch) — shared GSD planning |
{% else -%}
| `.planning/PROJECT.md` | GSD project definition |
| `.planning/codebase/*.md` | Pre-seeded codebase intelligence |
{% endif -%}
| `.cursor/` | Workspace-local Cursor config (populated by copier `_tasks` / GSD, refreshed on every `copier update`) |
